
Nitrogen Version 2.0.x

---

Nitrogen relies on the following software:

  - Erlang R13B03 or later (http://erlang.org)

  - SimpleBridge - Common interface to Erlang HTTP servers.
    Git Repo: git://github.com/rklophaus/SimpleBridge.git
    Tag: v1.1.0

  - mochiweb - HTTP Server (Optional)
    SVN Repo: http://mochiweb.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/
    Tag: 1.5.0

  - webmachine - HTTP Resource Server (Optional)
    git@github.com:basho/webmachine.git
    Tag: webmachine-1.7.3

  - yaws - HTTP Server (Optional)
    http://yaws.hyber.org/download/yaws-1.89.tar.gz

---

Javascript Libraries:
  - JQuery 1.4.2
  - JQuery UI 1.8rc2
  - Live Validation 1.3

---

Nitrogen is built and tested on a Mac running OSX Leopard in Firefox, Chrome, and Safari.
